<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Edit Profile - MySpace</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen">
    <nav
      class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white shadow-lg"
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between py-4">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold">
            <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-200 transition">MySpace</a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-6">
            <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-200 transition font-semibold"
              >Home</a
            >
            <a
              href="/profile/<%= currentUser.username %>"
              class="hover:text-blue-200 transition font-semibold"
              >My Profile</a
            >
            <a
              href="/profile/edit"
              class="hover:text-blue-200 transition font-semibold"
              >Edit Profile</a
            >
            <a
              href="/auth/logout"
              class="hover:text-blue-200 transition font-semibold"
              >Logout</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm">
            Welcome, <strong><%= currentUser.displayName %></strong>!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Edit Your Profile</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Customize your MySpace like it's 2005! üé®
        </p>

        <form method="POST" action="/profile/update">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 pb-2 border-b-2 border-blue-500"
            >
              Basic Info
            </h2>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <label for="mood" class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2"
                >Current Mood:</label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                id="mood"
                name="mood"
                value="<%= profile.mood || '' %>"
                placeholder="chillin, excited, nostalgic..."
                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <label
                for="location"
                class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2"
                >Location:</label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                id="location"
                name="location"
                value="<%= profile.location || '' %>"
                placeholder="Your city or state"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <label for="bio" class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2"
                >About Me:</label
              >
              <textarea
                id="bio"
                name="bio"
                rows="5"
                placeholder="Tell everyone about yourself!"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
              >
<%= profile.bio || '' %></textarea
              >
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <label
                for="profileSong"
                class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2"
                >Profile Song:</label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                id="profileSong"
                name="profileSong"
                value="<%= profile.profile_song || '' %>"
                placeholder="Artist - Song Name"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
              />
              <small class="text-gray-600"
                >The song that plays when people visit your profile
                (conceptually!)</small
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-purple-500"
            >
              üé® Custom HTML
            </h2>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-4">
              <p class="text-yellow-800 font-semibold">
                ‚ö†Ô∏è This is where the magic happens! Add your custom HTML here.
                Be creative!
              </p>
              <p class="text-yellow-700 text-sm mt-1">
                (Just like the old days - but be careful, it will render exactly
                as you type it!)
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <label
                for="customHtml"
                class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2"
                >Custom HTML:</label
              >
              <textarea
                id="customHtml"
                name="customHtml"
                rows="10"
                placeholder="<h3>My Cool Section</h3>
<p>Check out my awesome content!</p>
<marquee>Welcome to my page!</marquee>"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 font-mono text-sm"
              >
<%= profile.custom_html || '' %></textarea
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500"
            >
              üé® Custom CSS
            </h2>
            <div class="bg-pink-50 border-l-4 border-pink-400 p-4 mb-4">
              <p class="text-pink-800 font-semibold">
                ‚ö†Ô∏è Advanced: Add your custom CSS styles here!
              </p>
              <p class="text-pink-700 text-sm mt-1">
                Change colors, fonts, backgrounds - make it YOUR space!
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <label
                for="customCss"
                class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2"
                >Custom CSS:</label
              >
              <textarea
                id="customCss"
                name="customCss"
                rows="10"
                placeholder="body {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
}

.profile-container {
  border: 3px dotted hotpink;
}"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pink-500 font-mono text-sm"
              >
<%= profile.custom_css || '' %></textarea
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-200"
            >
              Save Changes
            </button>
            <a
              href="/profile/<%= currentUser.username %>"
              class="bg-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-200"
            >
              Cancel
            </a>
          </div>
        </form>

        <div class="mt-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-blue-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
            üí° Tips for Customizing:
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>
              ‚Ä¢ Use
              <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">&lt;marquee&gt;</code>
              tags for that authentic 2005 feel!
            </li>
            <li>
              ‚Ä¢ Add
              <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">&lt;blink&gt;</code>
              tags (they might not work in modern browsers, but it's fun to
              try!)
            </li>
            <li>
              ‚Ä¢ Embed images with
              <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded"
                >&lt;img src="url"&gt;</code
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              ‚Ä¢ Create tables with
              <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">&lt;table&gt;</code>
              for layout (just like old times!)
            </li>
            <li>
              ‚Ä¢ In CSS, try wild gradients, background images, and custom fonts
            </li>
            <li>
              ‚Ä¢ Change text colors with
              <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">color</code> and
              backgrounds with
              <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">background</code>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
